The paper deals with applying unsupervised learning algorithms to remote sensing data, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of feature extractors, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of natural class hierarchies, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
